-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1741444927819" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1741444927819"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Suchen Sie nach einem Schmuckstück, das mehr kann als nur funkeln – etwas, das Ihre Persönlichkeit unterstreicht, Ihre Stimmung hebt und Ihrem Alltag einen Hauch von zeitloser Eleganz verleiht? Diese <strong>Vintage Crystal Glanzohrringe</strong> sind mehr als bloße Accessoires; sie sind kleine Kunstwerke, reich an Charme und Strahlkraft. Jedes Mal, wenn Sie in den Spiegel blicken, erinnern sie Sie an Ihre eigene Grazie, Einzigartigkeit und Ausstrahlung – ein Schatz, zu dem Sie immer wieder greifen werden.</p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753003432" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753003432" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753020114" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753020114" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://83wwqjw917o5we3t-81568891219.shopifypreview.com/cdn/shop/files/3_0abd1e41-0c83-4649-a348-e676b2ef33d6_1296x.jpg?v=1755266744" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753025516" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753025516"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><b>1. Klassische Eleganz & zeitloser Charme</b></font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753059830" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753059830"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000">Kristalle stehen seit jeher für Reinheit, Licht und Schönheit. Mit diesen Ohrringen tragen Sie diese Aura der Eleganz überallhin. Das vintage-inspirierte Design verbindet Raffinesse mit einem Hauch Nostalgie – perfekt für Frauen, die Tradition und Stil gleichermaßen schätzen. Sie verleihen jedem Look das gewisse Etwas und ziehen bewundernde Blicke auf sich.</font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753190022" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753190022" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190023" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753190023" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/ce8aee12-945b-4168-b194-1337382edde7-ezgif.com-gif-to-webp-converter_120x120.webp?v=1755266776" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="480" height="480" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="480" natural-height="480" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190046" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753190046"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><b>2. Funkeln, das verzaubert</b></font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190025" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753190025"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000">Jeder Kristall ist sorgfältig geschliffen und poliert, um maximale Brillanz zu entfalten. Im Licht erstrahlen die Facetten mal glasklar, mal mit zarten Regenbogenreflexen. Ob zur schlichten Alltagskleidung oder zum eleganten Abendkleid – diese Ohrringe setzen immer ein strahlendes Highlight, das unvergessen bleibt.</font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753272291" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753272291" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272369" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753272369" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://83wwqjw917o5we3t-81568891219.shopifypreview.com/cdn/shop/files/2_e440b519-2dc8-4f7a-9d90-06fb8ae4d875_1080x.jpg?v=1755266744" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272327" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753272327"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><b>3. Leicht wie eine Feder, angenehm zu tragen</b></font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272326" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753272326"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000">Gefertigt aus hochwertigen, nickelfreien Materialien, sind diese Ohrringe nicht nur langlebig, sondern auch so bequem, dass Sie sie den ganzen Tag tragen können. Trotz ihres luxuriösen Funkelns sind sie federleicht – so mühelos, dass Sie fast vergessen, dass Sie sie tragen, bis Sie wieder ein Kompliment dafür bekommen.</font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753359383" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753359383" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753359364" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753359364" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://83wwqjw917o5we3t-81568891219.shopifypreview.com/cdn/shop/files/19ab5e7d-cfad-41da-973a-ce21b46cc967_1296x.png?v=17